Package gov.sandia.gmp.util.colormap

Class ColorRange

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.gmp.util.colormap.ColorRange
public class ColorRange extends Object
Represents a range of floating point numbers of [minVal, maxVal] and corresponding Colors on each end. Double values are placed into an appropriate range to be interpolated between the two Colors of an instance of this class.
Author:
jwvicke
